{"word":"παράγω","slug":"παράγω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>παράγω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:παρά\">παρά</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἄγω\">ἄγω</a></el>] ‘pass in the act of going’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp> pass by <a href='B:470 20:30'>Mt 20:30</a>; <a href='B:480 1:16'>Mk 1:16</a>; <a href='B:480 2:14'>2:14</a>; <a href='B:480 15:21'>15:21</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp> go away <a href='B:470 9:9'>Mt 9:9</a>, <a href='B:470 9:27'>27</a>; <a href='B:500 8:59'>J 8:59</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a></b> In imagery, with focus on disappearance<b> <a href='B:530 7:31'>1 Cor 7:31</a>; <a href='B:690 2:8'>1 J 2:8</a>, <a href='B:690 2:17'>17</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:παραγίνομαι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:παραδέδομαι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}